Map Data
========

The map data file:

docs/public/data/countries-110m.topojson

is derived from Natural Earth "Admin 0 - Countries", 1:110m.

Source:

https://www.naturalearthdata.com/downloads/110m-cultural-vectors/

Natural Earth states that all versions of its raster and vector map data found
on the Natural Earth website are in the public domain and may be used in any
manner.

Terms of Use:

https://www.naturalearthdata.com/about/terms-of-use/
